CrossFit W.O.D
Strength:
On A 14:00 Min Running Clock, Build Up for a heavy complex for the day:
1 Snatch Pull
1 Low Hang Squat Snatch
1 Squat Snatch

Metcon:
20 Min EMOM, For Max reps:
1.)	Double Unders
2.)	1DB Alt. Overhead Lunges #1x22.5/15
3.)	Sit-ups
4.)	WallWalks

CrossFit Endurance
For Time: (#10/6kg Vested)
800m run
50 Pull ups
100 Push Ups
150 Air Squats
800m Run
